<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#3ec28eb0b4b9c604ed790b4d102930e6>.
<#3ec28eb0b4b9c604ed790b4d102930e6> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/79c2ad4f-a216-4636-9714-713adc3c3a6a>;
