<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#f3543ad069b87e35154ce680699454a1>.
<#f3543ad069b87e35154ce680699454a1> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/d7568ec4-d9e0-4f8f-bf01-e9f672a79198>;
