<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#e99253b0e5d7bd56b610a26048d0802b>.
<#e99253b0e5d7bd56b610a26048d0802b> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://statistikdatabasen.scb.se/dataset/TAB1608>;
