    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/provenance> _:b0__80760.
_:b0__80760 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Källa: CAN:s nationella skolundersökning."@sv;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement>.
