<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#fac881a91090b66844080c64ff0f50f7>.
<#fac881a91090b66844080c64ff0f50f7> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://doi.org/10.5878/001444>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-23T06:26:36.797Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
